description: This skill has tips for how to get your best and healthiest hair possible. The user gets started by asking Alexa for awesome hair tips.  There are no prerequisites or special products needed.  I share a few products I particularly enjoy.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask awesome hair tips for a hair tip
Alexa, ask awesome hair tips to give me a hair tip
Alexa, ask awesome hair tips to tell me a hair tip
name: awesome hair tips
shortDescription: Ask awesome hair tips for tips on the best ways to care for your hair.
